Required Packages:

	uuid (default on many systems)
	lighttpd (for RESTful interface)
	scgilib (C binding for Simple Common Gateway Interface: to connect
		lighttpd with GDP; from http://www.xamuel.com/scgilib/;
		slightly modified and included with this distribution)
	cJSON (JSON library from http://sourceforge.net/projects/cjson/.
		It's possible that Jansson http://www.digip.org/jansson/
		is a better choice)
